                <text type="forecast_winds">Northerly 10 to 15 knots, reaching up to 20 knots in the west early in the morning. Winds turning west to northwesterly during the morning and early afternoon then becoming variable about 10 knots in the late afternoon.</text>
                <text type="forecast_seas">Around 1 metre.</text>
                <text type="forecast_swell1">Southwesterly 2 metres, increasing to 2 to 3 metres during the morning.</text>
                <text type="forecast_weather">Cloudy. 95% chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the evening.</text>
